snippet.textDisplay:
April 20 couldn't come any sooner. I've never been this impatient waiting for a comeback (I'm used to waiting a lifetime for most of my faves' comeback 😅) but for GOT7 I can't afford to be THAT calm. Maybe it has a lot to do with the fact that this is my first comeback experience with them and that, in itself, will definitely go down to my Aghase history. It'll be my very first milestone since entering the nest and I can't wait to give it my all.

I was late for 6 years. I'll never be late again even for 6 seconds.

Really, when did I learn to love GOT7 this much? And guess what? I'll mark my 2month anniversary of being an Aghase a day before their mv comes out. How frickin cool is that?
